Package joelib2.process.filter

Provides representating classes for the specialized filter options for molecular processing methods.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
Filter Interface definition for filter options for a molecule process.
 

Class Summary
ANDFilter Molecule process filter AND condition.
DescriptorFilter Interface definition for calling external programs from JOELib.
FilterFactory Factory class to get molecule process filter classes.
FilterInfo Molecule process filter informations.
HasAllDataFilter Molecule process filter for available descriptor entries.
HasDataFilter Molecule process filter for available descriptor entries.
NativeValueFilter Molecule process filter for native value descriptor entries.
NOTFilter Molecule process filter NOT condition.
ORFilter Molecule process filter OR condition.
RuleOf5Filter Filter to avoid molecules with a 'poor absorption or permeability'.
SelectionFilter Interface definition for calling external programs from JOELib.
SMARTSFilter Molecule process filter for SMARTS patterns.
 

Exception Summary
FilterException Molecule process filter exception.
 

Package joelib2.process.filter Description

Provides representating classes for the specialized filter options for molecular processing methods. This can be simple molecular filters, like molecular mass, number of hydrogen donors/acceptors, etc..
